// =============================================================================
// [PATCH: META-AD-LANG-FIRST + FAST-ONBOARDING]
// Context: Meta click-to-WhatsApp Ads sends exact language tokens first:
//   "English", "हिन्दी", "বাংলা", "ગુજરાતી", "मराठी"
